                                AutoPoint



              
        Autopoint enables you to select a window by simply moving the 
pointer over the window you wish to activate, without having to click on 
the select button. Double click on the AutoPoint icon to activate 
AutoPoint. To exit and return window selection to normal, either double 
click on the AutoPoint icon again or use the Exchange program (see 
Utilities/Exchange) to Kill it. 


